Package gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DialogListEntries
    In the DialogListEntries dialog the user can see and copy/paste the full list of entries.
    DialogMoveEntryToGroup
    This dialog let the player choose a new group for the selected element, and move the element there.
    DialogProgressBar
    This dialog show a progress bar with a label.
    DialogSearchFieldResults
    This dialog show all results of the search "Fields with the same value".
    DialogSearchLinkResult
    This dialog show all results of the search "Links to this entry".
    DialogSearchValuesResults
    This dialog show all results of the search "All values used in this field".
    DialogSearchValuesResultsList
    In the DialogSearchValuesResults dialog the user can double click on any entry to get the full list of entries.
    DialogSelectFiles
    Dialog which allow the user to select the files he want to load
    DialogSelectFiles.JFileContainer
    A JToggleButton which can hold a dat file data
    FrameEditor
    The main editor windows, with all entries and their fields.
    FrameMain
    The main window
    PopupMenuHandler
    This class show a popup for the selected field.
